{"tid":1037921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"思捷環球(00330.HK)中期虧損擴近86%至17.7億元","createTime":"2019-02-26T09:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T13:38:41.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b34de3f7552dc918074bfd77d11b1ce1470279b","tid":1037921,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"思捷環球(<a href=\"http://00330.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00330.HK&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=ab0eee6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00330.HK</a>)  -0.020 (-0.971%)    沽空 $4.59百萬; 比率 34.651%   公布截至去年12月底止中期業績，半年虧蝕17.73億元，較對上財年同期虧損9.54億元，按年擴大85.8%；基本每股虧損0.94元；不派中期息。期內收入67.66億元，按年跌15.8%；毛利34.71億元，按年跌18.4%。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，上半財年持續受到千變萬化的零售環境影響，當中消費者模式轉變及日趨激烈的價格競爭更構成衝擊。Esprit在品牌形象和產品吸引力方面欠佳，導致分銷渠道客戶流量減少，亦進一步加劇相應的壓力。新任管理層推出重大的變革措施，包括簡化公司工作流程並改善問責制，逐步淘汰虧損業務，強化品牌形象並凡事以客為本，及優化公司推出市場的產品。"},{"pid":"05b7e0a8571b43aad6b441194270351cbb6f77d1","tid":1037921,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkej.com/node/92948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F92948&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=8b0dcfd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkej.com/node/92948</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92867f0436604a93f38860c5edf64a2b4c747297","tid":1037921,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己玩死自己個Brand，牛屎蝗都唔撚屌了！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047bdd97ca994c2cad4e453a3ffe4ff97db1a8ec","t